I have the love of my life right here with me, and nothing in a game can compare to it.  And I would never, ever do anything that could potentially damage that relationship.  I've seen what investing too much of yourself in a character or an on-line relationship can do to a marriage.  It was the final nail in the coffin of my sister's marriage.  As far as I'm concerned, it's cheating.<br>
<br>
Now, if you and your SO have an open relationship, then go ahead, but be careful.  You never know when something like that will backfire on you.<br>
